{"id":4540,"date":"2015-04-25T16:45:56","date_gmt":"2015-04-25T21:45:56","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/?page_id=4540"},"modified":"2021-03-21T19:04:38","modified_gmt":"2021-03-22T00:04:38","slug":"epworth-sleepiness-test","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/epworth-sleepiness-test","title":{"rendered":"Epworth Sleepiness Test"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>All information you enter here is private.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>The test, phrasing and text below is The Epworth Sleepiness Scale by M.W. Johns.<\/p>\n<p>If the test says that you might want to check with your doctor, please do. I could have eliminated decades of waking up feeling hungover and exhausted if I had known about this earlier.<\/p>\n<p><strong>This test runs entirely in your browser and none of your information ever leaves your computer.<\/strong><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<p><strong>Instructions:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>How likely are you to doze off or fall asleep in the following situations, in contrast to feeling just tired?<\/p>\n<p>This refers to your usual way of life in recent times.<\/p>\n<p>Even if you haven\u2019t done some of these things recently try to work out how they would have affected you.<\/p>\n<form id=\"epworth\" action=\"javascript:ScoreTest();\" name=\"epworth\">\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Activity<\/th>\n<th>Chance of Dozing<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sitting and reading<\/td>\n<td><select name=\"answer\"><option value=\"0\">No chance<\/option><option value=\"1\">Slight chance<\/option><option value=\"2\">Moderate chance<\/option><option value=\"3\">High chance<\/option><\/select><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Watching TV<\/td>\n<td><select name=\"answer\"><option value=\"0\">No chance<\/option><option value=\"1\">Slight chance<\/option><option value=\"2\">Moderate chance<\/option><option value=\"3\">High chance<\/option><\/select><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sitting inactive in a public place (e.g a theater or a meeting)<\/td>\n<td><select name=\"answer\"><option value=\"0\">No chance<\/option><option value=\"1\">Slight chance<\/option><option value=\"2\">Moderate chance<\/option><option value=\"3\">High chance<\/option><\/select><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>As a passenger in a car for an hour without a break<\/td>\n<td><select name=\"answer\"><option value=\"0\">No chance<\/option><option value=\"1\">Slight chance<\/option><option value=\"2\">Moderate chance<\/option><option value=\"3\">High chance<\/option><\/select><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Lying down to rest in the afternoon when circumstances permit<\/td>\n<td><select name=\"answer\"><option value=\"0\">No chance<\/option><option value=\"1\">Slight chance<\/option><option value=\"2\">Moderate chance<\/option><option value=\"3\">High chance<\/option><\/select><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sitting and talking to someone<\/td>\n<td><select name=\"answer\"><option value=\"0\">No chance<\/option><option value=\"1\">Slight chance<\/option><option value=\"2\">Moderate chance<\/option><option value=\"3\">High chance<\/option><\/select><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sitting quietly after a lunch without alcohol<\/td>\n<td><select name=\"answer\"><option value=\"0\">No chance<\/option><option value=\"1\">Slight chance<\/option><option value=\"2\">Moderate chance<\/option><option value=\"3\">High chance<\/option><\/select><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>In a car, while stopped for a few minutes in traffic<\/td>\n<td><select name=\"answer\"><option value=\"0\">No chance<\/option><option value=\"1\">Slight chance<\/option><option value=\"2\">Moderate chance<\/option><option value=\"3\">High chance<\/option><\/select><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><input type=\"submit\" \/><\/p>\n<\/form>\n<p>This test is \u00a9 <a href=\"http:\/\/epworthsleepinessscale.com\/\">M.W. Johns 1990-1997<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>All information you enter here is private. The test, phrasing and text below is The Epworth Sleepiness Scale by M.W. Johns. If the test says that you might want to check with your doctor, please do. I could have eliminated decades of waking up feeling hungover and exhausted if I had known about this earlier. &#8230; <a title=\"Epworth Sleepiness Test\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/epworth-sleepiness-test\" aria-label=\"Read more about Epworth Sleepiness Test\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-4540","page","type-page","status-publish"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4540","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4540"}],"version-history":[{"count":70,"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4540\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":6014,"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4540\/revisions\/6014"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4540"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}